s to have occurred for no other purpose but the sake of discriminating because Manila english is just as comprehensible as standard American english. This is an example of where prescriptivism can be harmful and discriminatory towards demographics that do not speak the superstratum language. %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c Sources:%0a%3c https://www.latimes.com/health/la-xpm-2012-sep-18-la-me-english-only-20120918-story.html%0a%3c %0a%3c https://www.dialectsarchive.com/philippines-3%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
